abstract: >
  ContextFusion is a provider-neutral context compiler and optimization layer for LLM
  chat and agent workflows. It ingests heterogeneous sources, builds compact context
  packets, and compiles provider-specific requests under token and latency budgets.
keywords:
  - llm
  - context optimization
  - prompt engineering
  - agent workflows
  - mcp
  - retrieval
